ased products, fruit based products, soups, etc., as well as tea, coffee, lifestyle nutrition, ice-cream, and frozen desserts. The Other segment engages in export and consignment activities. The company is also involved in beauty salons, job work, real estate, and discharge trust business. Hindustan Unilever Limited was founded in 1888 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India."}}